Emma Stone and Ryan Gosling have been in three
films together, Crazy Stupid Love, Gangster

00:07:32.200 --> 00:07:33.200
Squad and La La Land.

00:07:33.200 --> 00:07:36.090
And Ralph Fiennes played Batman’s butler
Alfred in The Lego Batman Movie.

